To build the example you will need meson and ninja. If you have
python and pip installed, you can install them very easily by calling pip3 install meson ninja. Then, once the
example archive extracted to a ffmpeg-101 folder, go to this folder and call: meson setup build. It will
automatically download the right version of FFmpeg if you don’t have it already installed on your system. Then call:
ninja -C build to build the code and ./build/ffmpeg-101 sample.mp4 to run it.

